  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat",
    "Add the beef strips and cook until browned, about 5 minutes",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 3 minutes",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute",
    "Stir in the smoked paprika and cook for 1 minute",
    "Add the plain yogurt and stir to combine",
    "Add the fresh spinach and cook until wilted, about 2 minutes",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste",
    "Serve hot and enjoy"
